50|$|<b>The</b> <b>books</b> <b>was</b> first {{published}} in Bengali as Achena Ajana Vivekananda in November 2003 by Sahityam. Penguin Books translated and published <b>the</b> <b>book</b> in English in 2011. As of 2011, more than 100,000 copies <b>of</b> <b>the</b> Bengali version <b>of</b> <b>the</b> <b>book</b> <b>were</b> sold. <b>The</b> Bengali version <b>of</b> <b>the</b> <b>book</b> <b>was</b> a best-seller even in March 2014.|$|R
